Products designed to help small businesses grow and succeedBankingAccounts designed to meet business needsWhether you need just the basics or an account with extra features, First Citizens business banking options make it easy to find the right fit for your specific needs.Learn moreEquipment FinanceFinancial options for your business investmentsFirst Citizens gives you a variety of financing options for equipment. Offering customizable terms, we can also help you easily meet your tax, accounting and business cycle cash flow needs.Learn morePayment AcceptanceSolutions to streamline your transactionsWith services that make it easier to accept credit and debit card payments and enable you to deposit checks from your office, First Citizens can help improve your transaction efficiency, reduce your costs and boost your bottom line.Learn moreSBA LoansGrow your business, and your community, with an SBA loanAs a preferred lender of the U.S. Small Business Administration (SBA), First Citizens offers loans designed to help businesses grow. SBA loans can offer advantages over traditional loans, including lower down payments, longer repayment terms, and greater flexibility to use for a variety of businesses and purposes.Learn moreApproved to offer SBA loan products under SBA’s Preferred Lender programs.Online PayrollA simple, cost-effective payroll solutionFirst Citizens Online Payroll can help simplify and streamline your payroll processes, with features that automatically calculate withholdings, taxes and net pay — while also initiating direct deposits to your employees.Learn moreInsuranceCustomized options to protect what you’ve builtAs an independent insurance agency with more than 80 years of experience helping businesses, First Citizens Insurance Services can customize a risk management program to fit your business, and compare insurance options from a variety of carriers on your behalf.Learn moreFinancial solutions to support your growing businessCommercial Analysis AccountsCommercial Analysis AccountsConsolidates your business deposit accounts into a single relationship in order to manage cash flow more effectively.PayablesPayablesFrom payroll to wire transfers, payables solutions are designed to help you gain greater control of all of your payment transactions for maximum efficiency.ReceivablesReceivablesWith solutions that include ACH, eReceivables and Remote Image Deposit, First Citizens can help you streamline the collections process and manage incoming cash.ReconciliationReconciliationQuickly and automatically reconcile all checks paid against your First Citizens checking account to help save you time and money in keeping your records current.Industry Specific ExpertiseOur experienced business professionals can provide insight and guidance unique to these specific business sectors.Select industry… Property ManagementAgribusinessHealthcareNonprofitsDental PracticesLegal ServicesTrade AssociationsProperty ManagementAgribusinessHealthcareNonprofitsDental PracticesLegal ServicesTrade AssociationsBusiness InsightsStrategies for improving cash flowLearn how to better predict your income and expensesRead moreFinancing your businessFinancial options to support your business successRead moreManage personal finances as effectively as your businessLearn how our personal banking products and services can help you minimize costs and maximize your time. Learn moreProject your business cash flowCalculate Now Quick Links Order Checks*Remote Image DepositMerchant Card ProcessingWhat is the value of your business?Find bank routing and/or transit numberBusiness Visa® Credit Cards + View Legal Disclosures− Hide Legal DisclosuresFirst Citizens Bank, a division of First-Citizens Bank & Trust Company, Raleigh, NC.Insurance products are not insured by the FDIC or any federal government agency and are not a deposit or other obligation of, or guaranteed by, any bank or bank affiliate.* Upon clicking this link, you will leave the First Citizens Bank web