        Value Business Checking
        


$0 monthly maintenance fee1 if ONE of the following requirements is met:

$10,000 average daily checking balance
$15,000 minimum daily ledger balance in a related business savings account

Otherwise, a $25 monthly maintenance fee
A per item fee of $0.40 will be charged per item2 over 250.
A fee of $0.16 will be charged for each additional $100 coin and currency deposited over $7,500.
Minimum opening deposit: $100

Account openings and credit are subject to Bank approval.
1. e.statements are required to avoid a paper statement fee. 
2. Each item or transaction (other than non-PIN debit card transactions) which results in a debit or credit to the account is considered a separate item, including each check, paper draft, deposit, item deposited, wire transfer, electronic withdrawal/transfer and PIN-based transaction.





        Premier Business Checking
        


$0 monthly maintenance fee1 if ONE of the following requirements is met:

$15,000 average daily balance in a single Premier Business Checking account
$20,000 combined minimum daily ledger balance in Premier Business Checking, Business Savings, Commercial Money Market Savings, Premium Money Market Savings or CDs

Otherwise, a $35 monthly maintenance fee
A per item fee of $0.40 will be charged per item2 over 500.
A fee of $0.16 will be charged for each additional $100 coin and currency deposited over $10,000.
Minimum opening deposit: $100

Account openings and credit are subject to Bank approval.
1. e.statements are required to avoid a paper statement fee.
2. Each item or transaction (other than non-PIN debit card transactions) which results in a debit or credit to the account is considered a separate "item," including each check, paper draft, deposit, item deposited, wire transfer, electronic withdrawal/transfer and PIN-based transaction.





        Professional Business Checking
        


$0 monthly maintenance fee1 if ONE of the following requirements is met:

$30,000 average daily ledger balance in Professional Business Checking account
$75,000 combined minimum daily ledger balance in Professional Business Checking, Business Savings, Commercial Money Market Savings, or CDs
$10,000 in monthly First Citizens Merchant Services volume.

Otherwise, a $55 monthly maintenance fee
A per item fee of $0.40 will be charged per item2 over 1,000.
A fee of $0.16 will be charged for each additional $100 coin and currency deposited over $12,500.
Minimum opening deposit: $100

Account openings and credit are subject to Bank approval.
1. e.statements are required to avoid a paper statement fee.
2. Each item or transaction (other than non-PIN debit card transactions) which results in a debit or credit to the account is considered a separate "item," including each check, paper draft, deposit, item deposited, wire transfer, electronic withdrawal/transfer and PIN-based transaction.


+ View Legal Disclosures− Hide Legal DisclosuresAccount openings are subject to Bank approval.1. e.statements are required to avoid a paper statement fee.2. In WV, the maintenance fee is $10.3. On a daily collected balance of $1,000 or more, interest is paid at money market rates.  On balances less than $1,000, interest is paid at the Checking with Interest account rate.4. Interest is compounded daily on the daily collected balance, minus an amount based on the reserve requirements of the Federal Reserve.
