BusinessBankingMerchant Card Processing Banking MenuBusinessBankingMerchant Card ProcessingMerchant Card ProcessingExpand your customers’ payment options and streamline your operations with our payment solutionsContact Us
Your business is unique. And that means you need payment processing services tailored to how you do business.

Competitive pricing with no hidden fees.
No contract required
Instant authorization and next-business day funding for Visa®, MasterCard®, Discover and American Express transactions1 into your First Citizens deposit account
24-hour terminal support

Learn about our payment solutions:




Traditional Desktop Terminals

					Flexible retail solutions to meet the needs of brick and mortar merchants who prefer traditional desktop terminals.		
				

EMV ready terminals and peripherals
Process PIN debit as well as credit card transactions





Virtual Terminal

					Whether processing your customer's payment in person, by phone or by mail, your business can handle credit card and debit card payments seamlessly.		
				

Ideal for law firms, medical, dental, veterinary practices or any business that incorporates a PC into their payment process
View transactions in real time, set up multi-user capabilities and recurring payments, and spend less time resolving billing and collection issues
Sensitive cardholder data is stored on a Payment Card Industry (PCI) compliant secure server







e-commerce

					Your company website serves as your storefront and as a secure gateway for processing customer purchases, 24 hours a day. An e-commerce gateway can help your business provide an enhanced customer shopping experience.		
				

Manage and review transactions, configure account settings and download reports easily
Sensitive cardholder data is stored on a Payment Card Industry (PCI) compliant secure server





Mobile

					Your business is mobile — you and your employees are on the road, providing customers with service where they need it. Our mobile app allows you to process your customer's card anytime, anywhere.		
				

Ideal for businesses on the go
Accept payments with your iPhone® or iPad® anywhere you have cellular coverage
View transactions in real time and spend less time resolving billing and collection issues
Enjoy the highest level of card data encryption and security protocols when transmitting sensitive card data





Merchant Insights powered by Womply





Grow, Protect and Simplify Your Business
					Use the power of your data to make the most of your business. Make smarter decisions about marketing, operations, and employee management.
				

					Merchant Insights is an online tool that uses your merchant data to analyze your business and improve your business. With this tool you can:
				

Get a better picture of who your most profitable customers are. You can then use this knowledge to build a plan to acquire more like them.
Gain competitor intelligence. Learn what local businesses in your industry and market are doing to promote their company as well as any operational changes they are making to win customers from you.
Monitor social media. Gather and review customer feedback from an array of social media sites. Respond in real-time to show your appreciation and commitment to customer satisfaction.
Improve advertising effectiveness. Learn what geographic areas your customers spend the most money so you can focus your advertising budget where your customers are spending their time.


Learn more





PCI Compliance





					First Citizens and ControlScan help make it easier to understand and meet the requirements of PCI Compliance.
				

Learn more




